UPES CSE AI STUDY MASTER FILE
(YouTube + Chatbot Prompt Edition)
============================================================
Version: 14-Apr-2026
Purpose: Every subject -> every unit/topic -> ready copy-paste prompts for Gemini/ChatGPT.
Source Base: Your copied UPES handbook text (2023-2027 structure and syllabus blocks provided by you).


======================================================================
0) HOW TO USE THIS FILE
======================================================================

Daily Workflow:
1. Pick one subject and one unit.
2. Copy the exact prompt under that unit.
3. Paste in Gemini or ChatGPT.
4. Ask follow-up doubts until clear.
5. Solve 10-20 related questions.
6. Update your notes.

Prompt Customization Fields:
- [LEVEL] = beginner / intermediate / advanced
- [TIME] = 30 min / 60 min / 120 min
- [LANG] = English / Hindi / Hinglish
- [MODE] = theory / practical / interview / exam

Universal Follow-up Prompt (use after every topic):
"Now test me with 15 questions in increasing difficulty. First give me hints only. Then show final answers and common mistakes."


