1) PROGRAMME BLUEPRINT (DO NOT SKIP)
======================================================================

Programme: B.Tech Computer Science and Engineering with Specialization
Total Credits: 162

Credit Breakup:
1. Major Core (MC): 63
2. Basic Sciences (SCI): 26
3. Engineering Sciences (ENGG): 8
4. Major Elective (ME): 24
5. Life Skill Courses (LSC): 10
6. Exploratory Courses (EC): 15
7. Projects (PRJ): 16

Abbreviations:
1. L = Lecture
2. T = Tutorial
3. P = Practical
4. TC = Total Credits


