Cloud Fundamentals, Cloud Architecture and Deployment Models, Containerization and DevOps, Cloud Application Development, Cloud Security and Management (+ labs).

Track 4 Full Stack:
Frontend Development, Backend Development, Microservices and Spring Boot, Cloud Computing and Security, Container Orchestration and Security (+ labs).

Track 5 Cyber Security and Digital Forensics:
IT and Cyber Security, Ethical Hacking and Penetration Testing, Network Security, Digital Forensics, OS/Application/Cloud Security (+ labs).

Track 6 Big Data:
Big Data Overview and Ingestion, Storage and Analysis, Processing, Stream Processing, Big Data Search and Security (+ labs).

Track 7 Data Science:
