Track 8 IoT:
IoT Sensors and Microcontrollers, IoT Network Architecture and Protocols, Industrial IoT and ARM Embedded, Single Board Computers and IoT App Dev, Data Analytics for IoT (+ labs).

Track 9 Graphics and Gaming:
Intro to Graphics and Animation, Interactive Design and 3D Animation, Game Programming, Computer Graphics, AR/VR Development, Web Programming for Interactive 3D Graphics (+ labs).


