7) SPECIALIZATION TRACK PROMPT BANK (COURSE BY COURSE)
======================================================================

General Track Prompt:
"I selected [TRACK NAME] in UPES CSE specialization. Create full course-by-course learning map with prerequisite graph, practical tools, mini projects, major projects, interview questions, and portfolio roadmap."

TRACK 1 AI/ML course prompts:
1. Applied Machine Learning
Prompt: "Teach Applied ML from math intuition to implementation, feature engineering, model evaluation, and deployment basics with mini projects."
2. Deep Learning
Prompt: "Teach deep learning fundamentals, neural architectures, optimization and regularization with practical coding assignments."
3. Pattern and Visual Recognition
Prompt: "Teach pattern recognition and computer vision basics with feature extraction and classification workflows."
4. NLP
Prompt: "Teach computational linguistics and NLP pipeline from preprocessing to modern model intuition."
