10) FINAL INSTRUCTION
======================================================================

For every topic in this file, do not read only once.
Use this 5-step loop:
1. Prompt
2. Learn
3. Practice
4. Revise
5. Teach back

If you stay consistent with this system for 2+ years, your understanding will become deep, practical, and interview-ready.

